PrecisAppointment of a temporary Administrator, namely the Hon. William Arthur Esson, Chief Justice of the Supreme Court of B.C., who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of British Columbia over the course of a two-day period in August, 1990 (Aug. 20 & 21).
